snippet.title: Play Doh Surprise Unboxing Disney Stitch Toys Ice Cream Cupcake Cake Cocoa Candy Doughnut
snippet.description:
Toys For Kids Worldwide presents : Play Doh Surprise Unboxing Disney Stitch Toys Ice Cream Cupcake Cake Cocoa Candy Doughnut!

☆ ★ ♪ ❤ SUBSCRIBE ❤ ♪ ★ ☆
https://www.youtube.com/c/ForKidsWorldwidePlus?sub_confirmation=1

❤ Description ❤

Once more, we have Play Doh featured in a play set! These kinds of toy sets which use plasticine are always a great hit, as most kids really like to use play dough, considering it is absolutely great for developing creativity and imagination. The contents of this modeling clay for children, it seems, is a secret well kept, although we can tell that this is a dough for modeling various figures and characters as well as a sundry of objects, and contains both water and salt, as well as flour and wheat. We also need to say that this putty for playing has no peanuts or dairy products and that these kinds of toy sets are non-toxic, non-allergenic, and do not produce any irritation. It is also a great advantage that this dough can be used time and time again. And last but not least, it is definitely not a foodstuff!

And what is this play set about? It features Stitch from the Lilo and Stitch franchise films. Stitch is a so-called genetic experiment, an alien who looks like a blue koala bear. This is a character which is liked by no one expect for Lilo, who refers to him as a dog. In fact, he has superhuman strength and a very high IQ but he behaves like a child. This play set includes 5 boxes of Play Dough surprises. The first box with blue plasticine features the figure of Stitch with a wobbly head eating a cupcake. The next one, with red play dough, is Stitch sitting on a doughnut. The third, in yellow play dough, is the figure of Stitch with an ice cream cone in his hand. The fourth box contains blue play clay and a figure of Stitch and a mug of cocoa. And the penultimate box contains burnt orange clay with Stitch eating candy. And last but in no way least, the purple Play Doh, after being taken off, will display Stitch eating cake.

snippet.title: Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky High Bridge Jump Fisher-Price -  Unboxing Demo Review
snippet.description:
Watch Thomas complete his most breathtaking stunt yet in the Thomas and Friends TrackMaster Sky-High Bridge Jump from Fisher-Price. This Thomas & Friends train set breaks new ground by taking Thomas off the tracks and sending him soaring through the air, delivering speed, excitement, and motorized action like only TrackMaster train sets can! Inspired by the Thomas & Friends DVD, The Great Race, Sky-High Bridge Jump brings the movie to life with fast-paced, flying thrills. After a tall, spiral ascent with Harold the helicopter, Thomas speeds down a huge ramp and the velocity launches him into the air! Thomas soars for over two feet (0,6 meters) through the air before landing safely on the other side and continuing his journey. This one-of-a-kind Thomas & Friends train set also features a cargo hopper, waving flags, a barrel cargo piece, and removable Harold the helicopter.
- Complete Thomas & Friends train set includes motorized Thomas train, Harold the helicopter, cargo hopper, cargo piece, and full track layout with ramp and bridge jump
- Send Thomas under the bridge and up the spiral track
- When Thomas reaches the end of the track, Harold will lift him to the top of the ramp
- Thomas lands safely and continues his journey around the rails
- Tip the hopper to drop the barrel onto the tracks and Thomas will push it into the cargo area

Product description: This unique snap-together fashion kit comes with 260 pieces of funny jewelry beads in various shapes, sizes, designs, colors. Stimulate creativity Skills Do it by yourselves, make a beautiful decoration and puts you in a good happy mood. Girls snap the beads cultivate their hand-eye cooperation skill. Easy Snap Design for ages 3 and up. Beads are connected by insert. It is simple and convenient to disassemble and assemble. These beads are made from Recycled Toys Perfect for parties, rainy days, or just having fun at the house, you can be with this fully reusable jewelry kit. Make it, wear it, remake it, and wear it again. BPA Free, The toy beads are sturdy and well-made, it is non-toxic. Best gift for girls beading and jewelry making,also a good idea for birthday and Chritsmas gift.
Review by Davna (mom)- Once I received this DIY jewelry making kit I first looked at the packaging and I really like that it came in a plastic jar container that is really easy to open and close for Tiffany. The beads themselves are actually very well made, the quality  feels like beads that you would find at the Lakeshore Learning Store (except for HALF the price!) I love that the beads come in different textures, sizes and vibrant colors. It comes with a little booklet with pictures of some of the jewelry you can create which Tiffany liked to look at and recreated some of those accessories. The main thing I love about this toy is that it actually keeps both my girls entertained for LONG periods of time and it allows for their creativity to shine. We also use these to do some math, count and even create patterns! This is NOT meant for children under 3 as there are many small chocking hazard pieces BUT my youngest enjoys playing with them too under my CAREFUL supervision. It has been over a week now since we received this toy and since then both my girls have been playing with them DAILY! I highly recommend! 
CONS- The only con I found about this product is that some beads are harder to connect than others. Tiffany will be playing and be so nice and focused but then will have to come to me from time to time to help her snap some beads together which disrupts her (working) playtime. Tiffany is 4 years old so I know as she gets bigger she will be stronger and it will be easier for her to do completely on her own but if you have a 3 year old you will most likely have to play with them to help. My two year old already figured out which beads are harder to connect so she makes sure to only play with the beads that are easier to use lol
